				<td colspan="2"><span>Discs. Alt+C is your man and now called Combat Abilities.
<br />

<br />
UI. Shameless self plug. KKUI02 is out and aboout. Appropriate links are in the UI section.
<br />

<br />
LDoN. Deader than a week old necro pet. Better Augs and Items in GoD, OOW and DoN all round.
<br />

<br />
Others may disagree but /melody is my friend.
<br />

<br />
EXP. I have found DoN pretty friendly for exp. Earlier on maybe not, but the Hiistriy of the Isle quest usually nets me 3 aa's per mission taking about 1 1/2 to 2 hours to complete. Plus it gives DoN crystals, faction and the change for a couple of nice drops. (50HP aug and a Spellhaste V FT3 belt for teh casters out there)
<br />

<br />
Songs. If you have all your PoP songs then nto to worry, nothing really new from 66 to 70 other then the DoN proc songs. Just upgrades downgrades and upgrades.</span></td>
